The 2013 season was the [[Warrington Wolves]]' 18th season of the [[Super League]] era. Warrington lost the [[2013 Challenge Cup|Challenge Cup]] that they held due to a loss in the semi-final against [[Hull F.C.|Hull FC]]. They also made their second successive Grand Final appearance. However, they lost 30-16 against [[Wigan Warriors]] in the final.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/rugby-league/24384930|title=Super League Grand Final: Wigan Warriors beat Warrington Wolves|first=Matt|last=Newsum|work=[[BBC Sport]]|date=5 October 2013|access-date=23 February 2024}}</ref>

